                                   throws IllegalArgumentException,

        Create and show a dialog for adding Reaction with given JSBML Reaction object. If a user edits the reaction through this dialog, then a Reaction object will be returned. If not, null is returned.
        Parameters:
        reaction - the JSBML Reaction object
        Returns:
        the JSBML Reaction object if the reaction is edited
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - the illegal argument exception
